name: Spring Inn ad
note:
<desc:-------------------------------------------------------
   
Are you planing to stay in Zalesje? You can get a cosy room
in the Spring Inn. Located right by the northern entrance 
to the village.
   
------------------------------------------------------->

name: Tavern ad
note:
<desc:-------------------------------------------------------
   
Are you feeling long? Then come to the "Doggy's song"!
Right by the bridge, where people laugh, drink and play.
   
------------------------------------------------------->

name: Land for sale
note:
<desc:-------------------------------------------------------
   
The beautiful house on a large property is up for sale. 
Located near the count's mansion and just north of the 
scaffold. There is everything needed for a normal life: 
wonderful house, well, toilet, henhouse, vegtable garden 
and apple tree. 
   
The house has been left fully furnished by the former 
owner. If you want to purchase or rent, contact the chief.
   
------------------------------------------------------->

name: Bathhouse ad
note:
<desc:-------------------------------------------------------
   
Our public bathhouse is open in the village from morning 
until night. Hot steam, clear water and an invigorating 
birch leaf massage.
    
Wash and cheer up in good company 
for a reasonable price.
   
------------------------------------------------------->

name: Kittens for sale
note:
<desc:-------------------------------------------------------
   
I'm selling my brother's kittens. Almost free.
   
Please, take these cute fluffy ones, you will love them, 
I guarantee it.
   
From my jewelry counter is at the southern entrance.
   
------------------------------------------------------->

name: Literacy lessons
note:
<desc:-------------------------------------------------------
   
Do you need a quality capital scribe with great life 
experience and an excellent skill set? well as you may 
have guessed, I'm already here, in your village!
   
I'm prepared to teach anyone to read and write for a 
modest sum.
Girls will get a great discount.
   
Hurry up!
   
------------------------------------------------------->
